 America - Harvard Film Archive|publisher=|accessdate=14 January 2017}}</ref> |1989 |- |''[[J'accuse (1919 film)|J'accuse]]'' <ref name="warchild.ca"/> |1919 |- |''[[Jacob's Ladder (1990 film)|Jacob's Ladder]]'' <ref>{{cite web|url=http://peoplesworld.org/jacob-s-ladder-a-timely-film/|title=Jacobs Ladder a timely film|date=14 June 2002|publisher=|accessdate=14 January 2017}}</ref> |1990 |- |''[[Johnny Got His Gun (film)|Johnny Got His Gun]]'' <ref name="books.google.be"/> |1971 |- |''[[Journey's End]]'' <ref name="books.google.be"/> |1930 |- |''[[Joyeux Noël]]'' <ref name="nytimes">{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/movies/movie/327278/Joyeux-No-l/overview|website=The New York Times|title=A Christmas Truce Forged by Germans, French and Scots - The New York Times|accessdate=6 March 2017}}</ref> |2005 |- |''[[Kameradschaft]]'' <ref name="books.google.be"/> |1931 |- |''[[Kanał|Kanal]]'' <ref>{{cite web|url=https://books.google.be/books?id=jIDgWXZpBYkC&pg=PA141&lpg=PA141&dq=kanal%201956%20anti-war#v=onepage&q=kanal%201956%20anti-war|title=War and Film|first=James|last=Chapman|date=1 June 2008|publisher=Reaktion Books|accessdate=14 January 2017|via=Google Books}}</ref> |1956 |- |''[[Kelly's Heroes]]'' {{citation needed|date=November 2015}} |1970 |- |''[[King and Country]]'' <ref name="bfi"/> |1964 |- |''[[King of Hearts (1966 film)|King of Hearts]]'' <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2007/05/31/AR2007053102324.html|title=Jean-Claude Brialy, 74; French Actor of New Wave Films|first=Adam|last=Bernstein|date=1 June 2007|publisher=|accessdate=14 January 2017|via=washingtonpost.com}}</ref> |1966 |- |''[[King Rat (film)|King Rat]]'' {{citation needed|date=November 2015}} |1965 |- |''[[Ladybug Ladybug (film)|Ladybug Ladybug]]'' <ref name="nytimes2">{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/movies/movie/98568/Ladybug-Ladybug/overview|website=The New York Times|title=Movies - The New York Times|accessdate=6 March 2017}}</ref> |1963 |- |''[