{{Infobox book | name = Tilt-a-Whirl | image = Tilt-a-Whirl (novel).jpg | author = [[Chris Grabenstein]] | genre = [[Mystery fiction]], [[Thriller (genre)|Thriller]] | published = 2005 | publisher = [[Carroll & Graf Publishers|Carroll & Graf]] | isbn = 978-0-786-71781-1 | alt = Tilt-a-Whirl | pages = 321 | website = {{URL|http://www.chrisgrabenstein.com/adults/tilt.php|Tilt-a-Whirl}} | awards = [[Anthony Award|Anthony Award for Best First Mystery]] (2006) }}
'''Tilt-a-Whirl''' is a book written by [[Chris Grabenstein]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.barnesandnoble.com/w/tilt-a-whirl-chris-grabenstein/1100190312|title=Tilt-a-Whirl (John Ceepak Series #1)|last=Noble|first=Barnes &|website=Barnes & Noble|language=en|access-date=2017-03-22}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.chrisgrabenstein.com/adults/tilt.php|title=Author Chris Grabenstein: Books for Adults!|last=www.xuni.com|website=www.chrisgrabenstein.com|language=en-US|access-date=2017-03-22}}</ref> and published by [[Carroll & Graf Publishers|Carroll & Graf]]<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.co.in/books/about/Tilt_a_Whirl.html?id=RBEYo5y4TZcC&redir_esc=y|title=Tilt a Whirl|last=Grabenstein|first=Chris|date=2006-01-01|publisher=Carroll & Graf|isbn=9780786717811|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.publishersweekly.com/978-0-7867-1584-8|title=Fiction Book Review: Tilt-a-Whirl by Chris Grabenstein, Author . Carroll & Graf $23.95 (321p) ISBN 978-0-7867-1584-8|work=PublishersWeekly.com|access-date=2017-03-22|language=en}}</ref> on 20 September 2005, which later went on to win the [[Anthony Award]] for Best First Mystery in 2006.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.bouchercon.com/anthony-awards/winners-and-nominees/2000s/|title=Winners and Nominees 2000s|date=2015-09-22|work=Bouchercon|access-date=2017-03-22|language=en}}</ref>
